{
  "stem": "26728.6",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the inmates jumped over the wall again with 45s.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And anybody that was still alive they shot out there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And there are pictures in there about this whole thing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That really blew me away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, I did-- I was-- I was afraid, number one, for myself.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- I didn't feel any pity, per se.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't think, those poor bastards.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They-- I knew-- I knew they were POWs, but I was so enraged that I did-- I-- I guess without giving it a lot of thought, I th-- I felt probably basically that those bastards deserved it.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that's as far as it went, just on my part.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Can I interrupt for a moment?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Americans.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Americans.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Two squads of Americans have mounted these 30-caliber machine guns, which is the smallest machine gun.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's a weapon that has to be mounted on a tripod.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there's one in the street, in this street.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, it's a street, but not a street like you'd think of as a street.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was a building across the street from-- from where the wall was.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there's another gun on top of that, kind of like a mezzanine, with a crew shooting these German SS and [INAUDIBLE] guards.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "What they had done, they had surrendered, taken them into the hospital for safekeeping, and as a place where they knew they could control them.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this had all happened after the fire fight, you know, where the infantry had been fired on and had to kill these SS guards from the towers.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they killed them because they were fired on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They didn't kill him them because-- you know, the firefight lasted maybe 45 seconds.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But when they surrendered, they went ahead and killed them anyway.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
